attribute.description:
XML markup in the form:
				<pre>
				&lt;preferences&gt;
					&lt;preference&gt;
						&lt;name&gt;&lt;/name&gt;
						&lt;value&gt;&lt;/value&gt;
					&lt;/preference&gt;
				&lt;/preferences&gt;
				</pre>
				This value is persisted in the Liferay database when the embedded portlet is rendered for the first time.
